h2.heading.heading--secondary#enhanced Basic Dropdown

p.paragraph.
  The dropdown is used for a single selection out of a list.

.example(data-example-relative-base=relative('/'))
  include ../includes/example-header.jade
  .example__content
    .example__border
      .example__bracket.example__bracket--topleft
      .example__bracket.example__bracket--bottomright
      iframe.example__iframe
      .example__html
        include:ignorefrontmatter ./snippets/dropdown-basic.jade

.toggle
  .toggle__button(data-info, data-target='#code-basic')
    svg.icon-svg.toggle__icon
      use(xlink:href=relative('/images/icons.svg#source'))
    span See code
  .toggle__content#code-basic
    .tab-panel(data-tab, data-tab-default='html')
      .tab-panel__header
        .tab-panel__header__tabs
          .tab-panel__header__tab(data-tab-toggle='html') HTML
          .tab-panel__header__tab(data-tab-toggle='js') JavaScript
      .tab-panel__content
        .tab-panel__content__tab(data-tab-content='html')
          .tab-panel__content__tab__fullwidth-content
            .highlight: pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
              :highlight
                <div data-dropdown="data-dropdown" class="dropdown">
                  <div class="dropdown__label"></div>
                  <select class="dropdown__select">
                    <option>Schweiz</option>
                    <option>Regenbogenland</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
        .tab-panel__content__tab(data-tab-content='js')
          p.paragraph.
            Our jQuery plugin adds the
            <code>dropdown--js</code> modifier and handles
            keyboard events.

          p.paragraph.
            Activate the functionality with the data-* API
          .tab-panel__content__tab__fullwidth-content
            .highlight: pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
              include:highlightcode ./snippets/dropdown-basic.jade

h3.heading.heading--tertiary UX Checklist

ul.checklist
  li.checklist__item
    :markdown
      Generally, if you have less than 5 options, a <a class="link" href="./segmented-control.html">segmented control</a> might be the better option.
  li.checklist__item On mobile devices, use native dropdown pickers.

